#
# Bug#25054104 DATA DICTIONARY INITIALIZATION FAILS WHEN USING BINARY
# CHARSETS
#
# Note that this test also tests dictionary initialization
# using .opt file with --character_set_server=binary
# --character_set_filesystem=binary --collation_server=binary
